high_descs: Turn right then face the sink on your left.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter to your right.
Slice the bread on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink to your left.
Place the knife in the fridge and close it.
Turn around and face the counter with the bread on your right.
Take a slice of bread from the counter in front of you.
Turn around then face the fridge to your left.
Place the bread in the fridge for a bit then take it out.
Turn around and face the counter to your right.
Place bread on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place cold bread on the counter.

high_descs: turn right. Go forward a few steps. Turn left. Go to the sink.
Pick up the knife. Turn left.
Go straight towards the potato on the right.
Cut the potato into slices.
Turn around and go straight a few paces. Turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the knife inside of the fridge. Close the fridge.
Go back to the counter where the potato was cut.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Put the slice in the fridge where the knife was put.
Let the slice cool for a few seconds.
Take the slice back out of the fridge.
Put the slice back where the potato was cut.
anns.task_desc: Cut a potato and cool it down.
